### Marking Complete
To mark a follow-up complete:
- `/followup done: [person] [keyword]` ‚Äî Marks matching item as ‚úÖ Done
- During `/close` ‚Äî Prompted to review open items

### Behavior Summary
1. Parse person and topic from input
2. Normalize person name against people.md
3. **Check for duplicates** (same person + similar topic)
4. If duplicate found ‚Üí prompt for merge/keep/replace/skip
5. If merge selected ‚Üí update existing entry with new context
6. If no duplicate ‚Üí add new row to Open Follow-Up Items
7. Confirm: "Added follow-up: [Person] ‚Äî [Topic]" or "Updated follow-up: [Person] ‚Äî [Merged topic]"

