## `/escalate [issue]` ‚Äî Draft Escalation Communication

When the user types **`/escalate [brief description]`**, draft a professional escalation.

### Conversation Flow
1. "What's the issue?" (if not provided inline)
2. "What's the business impact?" (timeline, revenue, customer, team)
3. "What have you already tried?"
4. "Who are you escalating to?" (manager, peer, external)
5. "What action do you need from them?"

